013 Missioner's Complaint \u2013 Churches not Doing Enough|work=[[The Mercury (Hobart)|The Mercury]]|publisher=[[John George Davies|Davies Brothers Ltd]]|date ={{date|1935-01-22}}|publication-place=Hobart, Tasmania|p=7|accessdate={{date|2020-04-04}}|via=[[National Library of Australia]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"djenidi-2008-p218\">{{ref|djenidi-2008|\u03ba}} Dejenidi 2008, p. 218, footnote 621</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"barwick-p186\">{{ref|barwick-1995|\u03b2}} Barwick 1995, p. 186</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"western-age-1934-p4\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article137139411|work=Western Age|publication-place=Dubbo, NSW|title=Wily Aborigines|p=4|date={{date|1934-03-09}}|via=National Library of Australia}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"barwick-p187\">{{ref|barwick-1995|\u03b2}} Barwick 1995, p. 187</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"inverall-times-1938-p1\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article185394992|work=The Inverell Times|publication-place=NSW|title=Manager Dismissed|p=1|date={{date|1938-12-19}}|via=National Library of Australia}} \n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"armidale-express-1938-p1\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article194168878|work=The Armidale Express and New England General Advertiser|publication-place=NSW|title=Manager Dismissed|p=1|date={{date|1938-12-19}}|via=National Library of Australia}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"argus-1939-p2\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article12106282|title=NSW Mission Station \u2013 Man Convicted|date={{date|1939-03-11}}|work=[[The Argus (Australia)|The Argus]]|via=National Library of Australia|p=2}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"shepparton-advertiser-1939-p2\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article187750201|title=Mission Natives Frightened|date={{date|1939-03-13}}|work=Shepparton Advertiser|publication-place=Melbourne|via=National Library of Australia}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ferguson-letter-dubbo-liberal-p4\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article135929491|work=The Dubbo Liberal and Macquarie Advocate|de