 (TV series)|The Super]]'' || Janice || Episode: \"The Matchmaker\"<ref name=\":5\">{{Cite book|title=My Mother was Nuts: A Memoir|last=Marshall|first=Penny|publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|year=2012|isbn=|location=|pages=103\u2013109}}</ref>\n|-\n|1972 || ''[[The Bob Newhart Show]]'' || Stewardess || Episode: \"Fly the Unfriendly Skies\"<ref name=\"variety-18dec2018\" />\n|-\n|1972 || ''[[The Crooked Hearts]]'' || Waitress || Television film<ref name=\":5\" />\n|-\n|1972 || ''The Couple Takes a Wife'' || Paula || Television film<ref name=\":5\" />\n|-\n|1973 || ''[[Banacek]]'' || Receptionist || Episode: \"The Greatest Collection of Them All\"\n|-\n|1974\u20131975 || ''[[Friends and Lovers (TV series)|Paul Sand in Friends and Lovers]]'' || Janice Dreyfuss || 14 episodes<ref name=\"variety-18dec2018\" />\n|-\n|1974\u20131976 || ''[[The Mary Tyler Moore Show]]'' || Toni / Paula Kovacs || Episodes: \"I Was a Single for WJM\", \"Murray in Love\", \"Menage-a-Lou\"<ref name=\"variety-18dec2018\" />\n|-\n|1975 || ''[[Let's Switch!]]'' || Alice Wright || Television film<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=7sMBAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA138&dq=lets+switch+penny+marshall#v=onepage&q=lets%20switch%20penny%20marshall&f=false|title=New York Magazine|last=LLC|first=New York Media|date=April 22, 1985|publisher=New York Media, LLC|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|1975 || ''Wives'' || Connie || Television film\n|-\n|1975 || ''[[Chico and the Man]]'' || Anita Cappuccino || Episode: \"Chico and the Van\"<ref name=\":5\" />\n|-\n|1975 || ''[[Saturday Night Live]]'' || Herself || Episode: \"Rob Reiner\"<ref name=\":3\" />\n|-\n|1975\u20131979 || ''[[Happy Days]]'' || Laverne DeFazio || 5 episodes<ref name=\"variety-18dec2018\" />\n|-\n|1976 || ''[[Good Heavens]]'' || || Episode: \"Take Me Out to the Ball Game\"<ref>{{Cite book|title=Single Season Sitcoms, 1948-1979: A Complete Guide|last=Leszczak|first=Bob|publisher=McFarland|year=2012|isbn=|location=|pages=59}}</ref>\n|-\n|1976\u20131983 