lls)]]\n[[Category:Deaths from diabetes]]\n[[Category:Film directors from New York City]]\n[[Category:People from the Bronx]]\n[[Category:University of New Mexico alumni]]\n[[Category:American voice actresses]]\n[[Category:Women television directors]]\n[[Category:Cancer survivors]]\n[[Category:American women film producers]]\n[[Category:Actresses of German descent]]\n[[Category:Sports spectators]]\n", "name_user": "Moe1810", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eAs actress", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Penny_Marshall"}
